{"word":"G4422 - πτοέω - ptoéō - pto-eh'-o - Frighten","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πτοέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>ptoéō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>pto-eh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Frighten"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பயப்படு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to terrify"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> Probably akin to the alternate of <a href=\"#/G4098 - πίπτω - píptō - pip'-to/4098\">G4098</a> (through the idea of causing to <i>fall</i>) or to <a href=\"#/G4072 - πέτομαι - pétomai - pet'-om-ahee/4072\">G4072</a> (through that of causing to <i>fly</i> away); to <i>scare:</i> - frighten."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"}]}